        <span class="bbi-mono">What's included</span>
      </div>
      <h2>More than drop-off &mdash; your staff walks in to a finished workspace.</h2>
      <div class="lp-intro__body">
        <p>Brant Business Interiors is the family-run Ontario office furniture dealer most buyers know us by. The legal entity behind our OECM agreement is <b>Brant Basics</b> &mdash; same team, same address at 296 George St N, Peterborough. Family-owned since 1964; we install with our own people, not a freight contractor. The crew that quotes your job is the crew that shows up at your dock.</p>
        <p>Every order &mdash; single chair, full office, or multi-site OECM rollout &mdash; ships with coordinated delivery windows, white-glove in-room placement, full assembly and levelling, and packaging removal once the job is complete. For larger fit-outs, our project coordinators manage staging, sequencing, and after-hours or weekend site access to minimize disruption to operating clinics, occupied schools, and live municipal offices.</p>
        <p>Ontario coverage for delivery and install. Western Canada coverage for install &mdash; we ship freight from the manufacturer to your Western site and dispatch our install crew. Quote, freight, install, and warranty all handled by the same Ontario account team.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

