        </div>
        <div class="lp-diff-card">
          <div class="lp-diff-card__icon"></div>
          <h3 class="lp-diff-card__title">After-hours &amp; weekend installs</h3>
          <p class="lp-diff-card__body">For occupied clinics, school summer windows, evening completions in live municipal offices, and 24/7 hospital units. We schedule around your operations, not the other way around.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="lp-diff-card">
