      <div class="lp-howto__head">
        <p class="lp-howto__eyebrow bbi-mono">How delivery scheduling works</p>
        <h2>Three steps from PO to finished workspace.</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="lp-howto__steps">
        <article class="lp-howto__step">
          <span class="lp-howto__step-num">Step 01</span>
          <h3 class="lp-howto__step-title">Quote names lead times per line</h3>
          <p class="lp-howto__step-body">Your itemised quote flags lead time and install scope on every line. Stock items ship in 1&ndash;2 weeks; custom builds run 6&ndash;12 weeks. We confirm the install window before you cut the PO.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="lp-howto__step">
