          <h3 class="lp-howto__step-title">We schedule with your facilities team</h3>
          <p class="lp-howto__step-body">Dock access, elevator bookings, security clearance, after-hours or weekend windows for occupied spaces. Our project coordinator works directly with your facilities lead &mdash; one call, no surprises on delivery day.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="lp-howto__step">
          <span class="lp-howto__step-num">Step 03</span>
          <h3 class="lp-howto__step-title">Our crew delivers, installs, clears debris</h3>
          <p class="lp-howto__step-body">In-room placement, full assembly, levelling, sign-off walk-through. All packaging removed the same day. Old furniture removal as a line item if needed (see <a href="/pages/relocation">Relocation Management</a>).</p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

