  {%- comment -%} FAQ {%- endcomment -%}
  <section class="lp-faq">
    <div class="lp-faq__inner">
      <div class="lp-faq__head">
        <div class="lp-faq__eyebrow">
          <span class="bbi-mono">Common questions</span>
        </div>
        <h2>Delivery &amp; installation — FAQ</h2>
      </div>
      <ul class="lp-faq__list">
        <li class="lp-faq__item">
          <button class="lp-faq__q" aria-expanded="false">
            What areas do you deliver to?
            <span class="lp-faq__q-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          </button>
          <div class="lp-faq__a">
            <p>We deliver throughout Ontario, with primary coverage across Southern and Central Ontario. This includes the Greater Toronto Area, Peterborough, Barrie, Hamilton, Ottawa, Kingston, and surrounding regions. For projects outside Southern Ontario, contact us to confirm delivery availability and lead times.</p>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="lp-faq__item">
          <button class="lp-faq__q" aria-expanded="false">
            Does installation require a separate quote?
            <span class="lp-faq__q-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          </button>
          <div class="lp-faq__a">
            <p>Professional assembly and installation is included with most orders at no additional charge. For large-scale fit-outs or projects requiring after-hours installation, we'll note any additional costs in your quote upfront. There are no surprise fees.</p>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="lp-faq__item">
          <button class="lp-faq__q" aria-expanded="false">
            How far in advance do you schedule delivery?
            <span class="lp-faq__q-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          </button>
          <div class="lp-faq__a">
            <p>Lead times vary by product and manufacturer. Stock items typically deliver within 1–2 weeks. Custom or made-to-order pieces range from 4–12 weeks depending on the manufacturer. We confirm your delivery window at order confirmation and provide advance notice before delivery day.</p>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="lp-faq__item">
          <button class="lp-faq__q" aria-expanded="false">
            Can you deliver to multiple floors or restricted access sites?
            <span class="lp-faq__q-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          </button>
          <div class="lp-faq__a">
            <p>Yes. We coordinate site access, elevator bookings, and dock scheduling in advance. For healthcare facilities, schools, and government buildings with access restrictions or security requirements, our project coordinator works directly with your facilities team to plan logistics.</p>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="lp-faq__item">
          <button class="lp-faq__q" aria-expanded="false">
            Do you offer old furniture removal?
            <span class="lp-faq__q-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          </button>
          <div class="lp-faq__a">
            <p>Yes. We remove and responsibly dispose of replaced furniture as part of our relocation and decommission services. Ask about this option when requesting your quote &mdash; we'll include it in the project scope as a line item. See our <a href="/pages/relocation">Relocation Management</a> page for more detail.</p>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="lp-faq__item">
          <button class="lp-faq__q" aria-expanded="false">
            Can you install after-hours or on weekends?
            <span class="lp-faq__q-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          </button>
          <div class="lp-faq__a">
            <p>Yes. After-hours and weekend installs are standard for occupied clinics, operating hospital units, live municipal offices, and school summer windows. Mention your operational constraints when you request the quote and we'll schedule the install around your schedule, not ours. No premium charged for off-hours work on most projects &mdash; we'll flag in the quote if your scope adds cost.</p>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="lp-faq__item">
          <button class="lp-faq__q" aria-expanded="false">
            What's your Western Canada install coverage?
            <span class="lp-faq__q-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          </button>
          <div class="lp-faq__a">
            <p>We ship freight from the manufacturer to your Western Canada site and dispatch our own install crew. That means you get the same in-room placement, assembly, levelling, and debris removal as our Ontario installs &mdash; not a freight-and-walk-away. Lead times include freight transit. Your Ontario account team coordinates start to finish.</p>
            <p>Outside Ontario and Western Canada? Call us &mdash; we'll confirm what's possible for your site.</p>
          </div>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

